(191, 3, 'A Simple Kombucha Recipe That Has Many Health Benefits', 'a-simple-kombucha-recipe-that-has-many-health-benefits', 'Kombucha is a delicious drink that has been around for thousands of years. It first brewed in China around 220 BC and traveled along the Silk Road to Korea and Russia. Today, this ancient fermented tea has become a favorite among fitness enthusiasts and influencers for being healthy and easy to make at home. In this blog, we’ll cover how to make the perfect Kombucha recipe in just 7 simple steps and explain its health benefits. ', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/191_aqf2FrAV8.png?updatedAt=1743675372001', 3, 'A Simple Kombucha Recipe That Has Multiple Health Benefits', 'Kombucha is a fermented tea beverage with probiotics and a tangy taste. Discover this step-by-step guide to prepare the Kombucha recipe at home.', 'Kombucha recipe, What is kombucha, how to make kombucha,​ best time to drink kombucha​, how often should you drink kombucha​, health benefits of kombucha', 1, '2025-04-03', '2025-04-03 10:19:44', NULL),
